 wonders what the beginner will make of the last paragraph on p. 21, implying, as it does, that Linnaeus is the author not only of the species iphicla but also of the genus Adelpha, which is wrong.

Anyway I read the book with interest and remain gratefully yours.





Vladimir Nabokov





TO: A. C. SPECTORSKY

TL (XEROX), 1 p.





Montreux-Palace Hotel

Montreux, Switzerland

April 14, 1971

